# class vs struct

## 区别
|区别|class|struct|
|--|--|--|
|默认访问权限|private|public|

## 上手
```cpp
class C1{
  int m_iAge;  // 默认私有
};

struct C2{
  int m_iAge;  // 默认公共
};

int main(){
    C1 c1;
    C2 c2;

    c1.m_iAge = 1; // Error: 'm_iAge' is a private member of 'C1'
    c2.m_iAge = 1; // Pass
    return 0;
}
```
